 style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-w=
idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;">will fund their teams</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Almost all top players play with sponsors. As =
a result, top teams at American tournaments, which consist of three pairs, =
or six players per team, follow a peculiar configuration: one wealthy spons=
or and five pros in the sponsor=E2=80=99s employ. Top sponsors pay $1 milli=
on or more to field their dream teams.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CImagine if you could pay LeBron James=
, Kobe Bryant, Michael Jordan and Shaquille O=E2=80=99Neal and you could be=
 the fifth guy,=E2=80=9D Aviv Shahaf, director of the Honors, said. =E2=80=
=9CAnd you were at a level that was decent but not NBA level. That=E2=80=99=
s basically what this is.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That=E2=80=99s basically what this is, except =
it=E2=80=99s bridge.</p>
